			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>Product Testing: Simulation, dissimulation, exasperation</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Malware simulators are not an appropriate basis for testing product detection capabilities. </div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
                <div class="wls-author with-avatar">
